Wikia,is,a,collaborative,publishing,platform,that,enables,people,around,the,world,to,discover,create,and,share,content,on,any,topic,Wikia,also,provides,the,LyricWiki,API,a,service,which,provides,users,with,lyrics,to,many,popular,songs,from,a,variety,of,artists,This,free,API,can,be,used,via,SOAP,or,REST,though,the,SOAP,functionality,is,currently,more,robust,Lyrics,can,be,returned,as,XML,JSON,HTML,or,plain,text,Authentication,is,optional,when,using,the,API,via,SOAP,and,not,available,when,using,REST,and,can,be,used,if,you,want,to,associate,any,webservice,changes,that,you,make,with,your,user,account,Please,note,that,due,to,licensing,restrictions,the,API,can,only,directly,return,a,small,portion,of,the,lyrics,directly,which,is,useful,for,determining,if,you,have,a,correct,match,All,responses,also,contain,a,URL,to,a,corresponding,page,with,the,full,lyrics